<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ucolick.org/~sla/leapsecs/nc1985wp7a.html">Summary of the US Working Group proposal</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://igscb.jpl.nasa.gov/mail/igsmail/2005/msg00114.html">Opposition to the change</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.cl.cam.ac.uk/~mgk25/time/leap/">Efforts to abolish leap seconds</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
